      <section id="about">
        <div class="container">
          <h2 class="mb-3">About Us</h2>
          <p>Our hospital is committed to providing the highest quality medical care and services to our patients. We
            have state-of-the-art equipment and facilities, and our staff is dedicated to providing compassionate and
            personalized care to every patient.</p>
          <p>Our hospital provides a wide range of services to meet the needs of our patients, including emergency
            care, inpatient care, and outpatient care. Our team of highly qualified and experienced healthcare
            professionals includes doctors, nurses, medical technicians, therapists, and support staff, all working
            together to provide the best possible care to our patients.</p>
          <p>We believe that patient satisfaction is paramount, and we strive to ensure that every patient has a
            positive experience when visiting our hospital. We are committed to continuous improvement, and we welcome
            feedback from our patients to help us enhance the quality of our services.</p>
          <p>Thank you for choosing our hospital for your healthcare needs. We look forward to serving you.</p>
        </div>


